					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">As a slight simplification of lidnariq's suggestion, ca65 has the * symbol which is the program counter position known at link time, letting you do this:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">mystruct: .byte 2 4 5 7 8<br />mystructlength = * - mystruct</div></div>

